    Home Button: Should return home when clicked.
    Account: Drops down a menu when clicked. 
        -If logged in, the dropdown menu should display the user's Name & Email
        -If "Your Books" is clicked, should redirect to renting-out.html page.
        -If "Rental History" is clicked, should redirect to rental-history.html page.
